txt.en: Azruthor can be found just outside the main tent of the camp at Tarlang's Crown.\n\nYou should defeat Azruthor and his allies for the good of Gondor.
Azruthor can be found just outside the main tent of the camp at Tarlang's Crown.\n\nYou have discovered Azruthor's whereabouts and should now confront him.
Azruthor merely glares at you - his eyes betraying a seething rage.\n\nAll is silent for a moment, but then he begins to speak.
Azruthor can be found just outside the main tent of the camp at Tarlang's Crown.\n\nYou should defeat Azruthor and his allies for the good of Gondor.
Do not allow Azruthor to regain strength
Azruthor can be found just outside the main tent of the camp at Tarlang's Crown.\n\nAzruthor has begun to retreat to regain strength, and cannot be allowed to do so.
Worn down by your assault, the Corsairs have left one of their horses unattended. It is now time to return to Dol Amroth with news of your victory.
After weakening the forces in Tarlang's Crown, the time has come to confront Azruthor and put an end to the Scourge's plans for the Anfalas.
Seek Azruthor in the camp at Tarlang's Crown
Azruthor can be found in the main tent of the camp at Tarlang's Crown.\n\nHarnion has asked you to confront and defeat Azruthor in Tarlang's Crown.
